   Aviation Weather Services
                            National Convective Weather Forecast (NCWF)

   Aviation Weather Services, Advisory Circular (AC) 00-45E, explains
   weather services in general and how to interpret coded weather reports,
   forecasts, and observed and prognostic weather charts. It is an
   excellent companion manual to Aviation Weather, AC 00-6A, which
   describes weather theories and hazards.

   AC 00-45E may be downloaded (PDF, 4.4Mb), or viewed here as smaller PDF
   files. You will need Adobe Acrobat Reader to view these files.

   [getacro.gif]
